 《猎人克莱文》首映票房 1100 万美元，是索尼出品的漫威电影中最低的https://www.nme.com/news/film/kraven-the-hunter-opens-with-11million-lowest-of-any-sony-productd-marvel-film-3822428?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kraven- 《猎人》首映票房 1100 万，是索尼漫威电影中最低的Surej SinghMon, 16 Dec 2024 06:03:41 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3822428 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>低于索尼今年另一部票房炸弹《网络夫人》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kraven-the-hunter-opens-with-11million-lowest-of-any-sony-produced-marvel-film-3822428">《猎人克莱文》首映票房为 1100 万美元，是索尼出品的漫威电影中首映票房最低的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/kraven@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony-pictures">索尼影业</a>的上一部<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/marvel">漫威</a>电影<em>《猎人克莱文》</em>首映周末票房收入创下 1100 万美元的历史新低。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-films-2024-3817632">2024 年 20 部最佳电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/box-office-kraven-the-hunter-bombs-worst-start-sony-marvel-films-1236247536/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Variety》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2024/12/15/kraven-the-hunter-suffers-worst-case-box-office-crash-at-11-million/"><em>《福布斯》</em></a>报道， <em>《猎人克莱文》</em>在美国的票房收入仅为 1100 万美元，预计上映前三天在海外市场的收入同样糟糕。</p><p>这将使<em>《猎人克莱文》</em>成为索尼表现不佳的漫威电影中销量最低的电影，其中包括 2022 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/morbius-review-jared-leto-marvel-3195082"><em>《莫比亚斯》</em></a>和今年另一部票房不佳的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/madame-web-first-reactions-call-it-an-embarrassing-mess-3586521"><em>《韦伯夫人》</em></a> 。然而，尽管<em>《韦伯夫人》</em>票房惨败，但<em>克莱文的</em>处境似乎更加艰难。 </p><figure id="attachment_3458081" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3458081" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3458081" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main.jpg" alt="猎人克莱文" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kraven-The-Hunter-poster-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3458081" class="wp-caption-text">亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊饰演“猎人克莱文”。图片来源：索尼/漫威</figcaption></figure><p>与<em>《猎人克莱文》</em> 1100万美元的票房相比，<em>莫比乌斯</em>的首周末票房为3300万美元，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/madame-web-bombs-at-box-office-with-one-of-worst-marvel-returns-ever-3589970"><em>韦伯夫人</em>则为2620万美元——后者被认为是当时漫威角色的最低首周末票房</a>，现在已被<em>克莱文</em>超越。</p><p>目前，在影院与<em>《猎人克莱文》</em>竞争的是两部票房巨制： <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>《魔法坏女巫》</em></a>和<em>《莫阿娜 2》</em> 。</p><p> <em>《猎人克莱文</em>》的拍摄预算为 1.1 亿美元，预计 12 月不会实现收支平衡。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-taylor-johnson">亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊</a>饰演主角，一位大型猎物猎人，由于与父亲的复杂关系（由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-crowe">罗素·克劳</a>饰演）。</p><p> <i>《猎人克莱文》</i>是索尼蜘蛛侠宇宙的第六部，继<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/venom"><i>《毒液》</i></a>三部电影<i>《莫比亚斯》</i>和<i>《蜘蛛侠》</i>之后。与该系列的许多前作一样，该片在上周五（12 月 13 日）电影上映前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kraven-the-hunter-is-getting-destroyed-by-critics-strange-and-sloppy-3821486">并没有受到评论家的好评</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="猎人克莱文 |官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I8gFw4-2RBM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/kraven-the-hunter-spider-man-review-b2663035.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《独立报》</i></a>在一篇严厉的一星评论中写道：“永别了，索尼的无蜘蛛侠宇宙。你死了就像你活着一样：奇怪而草率……剧本非常分散，并且插入了大量重新录制的对话，以至于场景之间甚至场景内几乎没有凝聚力。安息吧，索尼的漫威宇宙——你真的让人脑壳疼。”</p><p> <a href="https://lwlies.com/reviews/kraven-the-hunter/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《善意小谎言》</i></a>的评论一致认为：“这一切都非常愚蠢，”他们写道。 “如果这部电影的编剧、明星和导演稍微投入一点——就像<i>《毒液》</i>电影中那样——也许这不是一个问题，但<i>猎人克莱文</i>身上有一种严肃的气氛，这使得它成为一个无法挽救的艰难过程。暴力处决数量惊人，其中包括用捕熊器进行的处决。”</p><p>继<em>《猎人克莱文》</em>之后，主演亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊将于 2025 年 1 月在英国回归大银幕，并于圣诞节当天在美国回归罗伯特·艾格执导的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/nosferatu"><em>《诺斯费拉图</em></a>》。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750046" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750046" style="width: 1364px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750046" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson.jpg" alt="亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊" width="1364" height="866" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson.jpg 1364w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Aaron-Taylor-Johnson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1364px) 100vw, 1364px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3750046" class="wp-caption-text">亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊于 2024 年 4 月 22 日在伦敦。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Ian West/PA Images via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>今年，泰勒-约翰逊也被盛传将成为下一个詹姆斯·邦德。据报道，三月份泰勒-约翰逊<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/aaron-taylor-johnson-swerves-james-bond-question-3750028">在试镜中给制片人留下了深刻的印象，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-james-bond-been-offered-role-british-actor-aaron-taylor-johnson-3603268">EON Production 向他提供了这份工作</a>。这位演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/aaron-taylor-johnson-swerves-james-bond-question-3750028">在四月份被问及有关谣言的问题，但他回避了这个问题</a>，就像<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/aaron-taylor-johnson-bond-rumours-interview-3604533">他之前多次做过的</a>那样。他和制片人都没有证实或否认这一猜测。</p><p>前邦德演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pierce-brosnan">皮尔斯·布鲁斯南</a>也对潜在的演员阵容发表了意见，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pierce-brosnan-reported-new-james-bond-prick-3609690">表达了他对泰勒·约翰逊的支持</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kraven-the-hunter-opens-with-11million-lowest-of-any-sony-produced-marvel-film-3822428">《猎人克莱文》首映票房为 1100 万美元，是索尼出品的漫威电影中首映票房最低的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
妮可·基德曼 (Nicole Kidman) 透露，她在 2008 年生下第一个孩子后差点退出演艺圈https://www.nme.com/news/film/nicole-kidman-reveals-she-nearly-retired-from-acting-after-having-first-child-in-2008-3822422?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nicole-kidman-透露她在 2008 年生下第一个孩子后差点退出演艺圈Surej SinghMon, 16 Dec 2024 05:09:10 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3822422 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我当时想，‘好吧，我想我现在已经完成了’”</p><p>妮可·基德曼 (Nicole Kidman) 的帖子首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/nicole-kidman-reveals-she-nearly-retired-from-acting-after-having-first-child-in-2008-3822422">，透露她在 2008 年生下第一个孩子后几乎退出演艺圈</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicole-kidman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicole-kidman">妮可·基德曼 (Nicole Kidman)</a>透露，她在 2008 年生下第一个孩子后几乎彻底退出演艺圈——详情请见下文。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-there-be-the-perfect-couple-season-two-3797800">《完美情侣》会有第二季吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p> 2008年，基德曼与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-urban">基思·厄本</a>生下了她的第一个孩子，周日·罗斯·基德曼-厄本。同年晚些时候，她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">休·杰克曼</a>一起主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/baz-luhrmann">巴兹·鲁尔曼</a>执导的史诗爱情片《<em>澳大利亚》</em> 。现在，基德曼透露，在某个时刻，<em>澳大利亚</em>可能是她的最后一个电影角色。</p><p>基德曼在接受<a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/video/extended-interview-nicole-kidman/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>哥伦比亚广播公司新闻</em></a>宣传她的新片<em>《宝贝女孩</em>》时透露，2008年7月生下“周日玫瑰”后，她一度处于退出演艺圈的边缘，但在母亲劝说她不要退出演艺圈之前。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="妮可·基德曼谈拍摄《女婴》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lskoRLjZawY?start=280&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>基德曼在谈到想要全职专注于家庭时说道：“当我周日出生时，我想，‘好吧，我想我现在已经差不多完成了’。”我们住在农场里，那时我母亲说，‘我不会完全放弃。把一根手指放在里面。我说，‘不，不。我现在完成了。我受够了。&#39;她会说，‘听我说。继续前进。并不是说你必须做到你一直在做的水平，但我不会完全放弃。”</p><p>几个月后，基德曼开始拍摄<em>《九号》</em>和<em>《兔子洞》</em>等角色。自2008年以来，基德曼主演了多部广受好评的卖座电影，包括<em>《斯托克》</em> 、 <em>《铁路人》</em> 、 <em>《帕丁顿熊</em>》、 <em>《狮子》</em> 、 <em>《杀死圣鹿》</em> 、 <em>《牡丹花下</em><em>》</em> 、《海王》和<em>《北方人》</em> 。</p><p>据基德曼说，她母亲的建议来自“一位女性，她的一代人没有我这样的机会，而她为她的女儿们创造了这些机会。所以这可能是她小时候希望拥有的东西。” </p><figure id="attachment_3813924" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813924" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813924" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="妮可基德曼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_nicolekidman_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813924" class="wp-caption-text">妮可·基德曼于 2024 年 11 月 11 日抵达纽约参加 Netflix 动画电影《Spellbound》的纽约首映 图片来源：Yuki Iwamura 法新社 / Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>至于电视角色，基德曼出演了两季广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/big-little-lies"><em>《大小谎言》</em></a> 、 <em>《九个完美陌生人》</em> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-there-be-the-perfect-couple-season-two-3797800"><em>《完美情侣》</em></a>等。 <em>《完美情侣》</em>于 9 月在 Netflix 首播，并在该流媒体平台上大受欢迎。</p><p>该剧改编自艾琳·希尔德布兰德 2018 年的同名小说，讲述了一对夫妇在马萨诸塞州楠塔基特岛举行的奢华婚礼计划，但婚礼当天早上，婚礼当天早上，婚礼派对上的一名成员的尸体被冲到海滩上，婚礼计划因此而泡汤。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" id="37937655" title="完美情侣|官方预告片| Netflix" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uyD3tR6gvHs?feature=oembed&amp;enablejsapi=1" width="100%" height="392" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-gtm-yt-inspected-6="true" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p><p>妮可·基德曼饰演著名小说家格里尔·加里森·温伯里家族女族长，演员阵容还包括列维·施瑞伯、伊芙·休森、梅根·费伊、杰克·莱诺和达科塔·范宁。</p><p>基德曼接下来将主演 A24 色情惊悚片<em>《宝贝女孩》</em> ，该片将于 2025 年 1 月在英国电影院上映。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/nicole-kidman-reveals-she-nearly-retired-from-acting-after-having-first-child-in-2008-3822422">妮可·基德曼 (Nicole Kidman) 的帖子透露，她在 2008 年生下第一个孩子后几乎退出演艺圈</a>，并首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看 Soundgarden 幸存成员重聚西雅图的慈善演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-soundgardens-surviving-members-reunite-for-seattle-benefit-gig-3822416?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-soundgardens-surviving-members-reunite-西雅图福利演出Surej SinghMon, 16 Dec 2024 04:09:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsGrungeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3822416 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Duff McKagan 和 Shaina Shepherd 加入了他们的队伍，号称 Nudedragons</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-soundgardens-surviving-members-reunite-for-seattle-benefit-gig-3822416">《Watch Soundgarden》幸存成员为西雅图慈善演出重聚的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/soundgarden-nudedragons@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soundgarden">Soundgarden</a>的幸存成员以 Nudedragons 身份重聚，参加西雅图的一场慈善音乐会 - 请观看下面的演出片段。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/chris-cornell-best-songs-2073509"><b>Chris Cornell 歌曲：Soundgarden 和 Audioslave 主唱的最佳歌曲</b></a></li></ul><p>成员 Kim Thayil、Matt Cameron 和 Ben Shepherd 于 12 月 14 日在西雅图 Showbox 重聚，进行演出。乐队名称为 Nudedragons，是 Soundgarden 的变位词，与他们 2010 年重聚首张专辑时使用的名字相同。自1997年开始演出。</p><p> Nudedragons 成员与歌手 Shaina Shepherd 一起参加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/surviving-soundgarden-members-reuniting-as-nudedragons-for-seattle-benefit-show-3819386">第 13 届年度 SMooCH 音乐会，该音乐会帮助西雅图儿童医院无偿护理基金受益</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a>也与他们一起演唱了最后两首歌曲。</p><p> Nudedragons 和 Shaina Shepherd 演奏了四首 Soundgarden 曲目来拉开演出序幕：《Hunted Down》、《Outshined》、《Flower》和《Beyond The Wheel》。在最后两首歌中，他们邀请 McKagan 参与 Soundgarden 的《Kickstand》，并以翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mc5">MC5</a>的《Kick Out The Jams》结束了近 30 分钟的演出。</p><p>请观看下面由粉丝拍摄的 Soundgarden/Nudedragons 完整演出的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nudedragons (Soundgarden) 完整演出在西雅图 Showbox 与 Shaina Shepherd 进行 SMOOCH 现场直播 | 2024年4K" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9QCJ-vWuxuY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3> <strong>Soundgarden（Nudedragons）的套装是：</strong></h3><p><strong>谢娜·谢泼德《追捕》</strong><br /><strong>与谢娜·谢泼德 (Shaina Shepherd) 一起“超越”</strong><br /><strong>谢娜·谢泼德的《花》</strong><br /><strong>谢娜·谢泼德的《超越车轮》</strong><br /> <strong>Shaina Shepherd 和 Duff McKagan 的“支架”</strong><br /> <strong>Shaina Shepherd 和 Duff McKagan 合作的《Kick Out The Jams》（MC5 封面）</strong></p><p>在节目<a href="https://smoochforkids.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>上，乐队的表演被描述为“短暂的安可表演”。自主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-cornell">克里斯·康奈尔</a>2017 年去世以来，三位幸存成员只一起演出过两次。他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/spine-tingling-moments-chris-cornell-tribute-show-2432182">在 2019 年康奈尔大学的致敬演出中</a>一起亮相，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brandi-carlile-performs-soundgarden-tracks-live-with-surviving-band-members-3019633">2021 年与布兰迪·卡莱尔 (Brandi Carlile) 一起亮相</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soundgarden-audioslave-singer-chris-cornell-died-aged-52-2073457">2017年5月18日，康奈尔大学自杀身亡</a>。他今年 52 岁。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDir9yTJZoF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50p